THE GAME
--------

  'TriLights' is a Workbench game where the goal is to switch on
all the lightbulbs of a triangular shaped board. You play by
clicking on a lightbulb, this will toggle all the lightbulbs on
the same row and diagonally from where the lightbulb is located.

  When you complete a game board, TriLights displays a new board,
with more lightbulbs that have been switched on or off, and so
on...

  If you find that the game is too easy, you can try the 'Harder'
game by clicking on the 'Easy/Harder' toggle button...

  Complete each game board in the least amount of moves.

  Have fun!

